title: Whataburger Oh Whata Night
text:
5:00 p.m. Tuesday, Oct. 27, 2015 Categories 
Events, Fundraisers, Kids | Family On Tuesday, Oct. 27, Whataburger customers can show their support for the Canutillo High School basketball team by enjoying their favorite menu items, and 20 percent of Whataburger’s sales form 5 to 8 p.m. will be donated to the Canutillo High School basketball team. Whataburger’s “Oh Whata Night” will also include a photo booth onsite and the popular “Whataburger for a Year” drawing, where one customer’s name will be drawn to win the prize – a free Whataburger each week for an entire year.
